                     <interp inst="t18680817-654-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp> Stealing fifty-eight spoons, eight ladles, and other articles, value 100<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., of <persName id="t18680817-name-27" type="victimName">
